Attraction.sql: SELECT * FROM traveldb.`vw_/dashboard/product/attraction` WHERE UserID=? AND IF (? is null ,- 1, Status) = IF (? is null ,-1, IF(?='released',2,1)) LIMIT (?-1)*8, 8;

Counts.sql: SELECT cast(count(*)/8 as decimal(10,0)) as Count FROM traveldb.`vw_/dashboard/product/attraction` where  UserID=? AND IF (? is null ,- 1, Status) = IF (? is null ,-1, IF(?='released',2,1));
